# FreeCRM E2E Tests (Playwright)

Tests live in `tests/e2e`. Target is **`https://dev.itconnect.pl`** (set as `baseURL`; local Docker stack, WSL cannot reach `localhost`). Login: `admin` / `NewArgon2idAdmin#42` (see `login-credentials.mdc`).

## Layout & run
- `tests/<area>/<Module>/<feature>.spec.ts`, page objects in `pages/<Module>Page.ts`, auth in `fixtures/auth.fixture.ts`.
- The `playwright` binary often lacks exec perm → **always run via npm**: `npm run pw -- test <path> --reporter=list` (cwd `tests/e2e`). `npm run pw` = `node node_modules/@playwright/test/cli.js`.

## Auth & test skeleton
Use the `authenticatedPage` fixture (handles login):
```ts
import { test, expect } from '../../../fixtures/auth.fixture';
test.beforeEach(async ({ authenticatedPage }) => { /* new XxxPage(authenticatedPage); gotoList() */ });
```

## Module URLs & navigation
- List view: `/index.php?module=<Module>&view=ListView` — **omit `mid`/`parent`** (menu-id specific, env-fragile; ListView works without them).
- Switch saved filter/custom view by visible name via `#customFilter` (select2): `selectOption({ label: 'Wszystkie' }, { force: true })`; its native `change` reloads the list.

## List view selectors
- Table: `table.listViewEntriesTable`. Data rows: `tbody tr.listViewEntries`.
- Inline search inputs/selects: `.listSearchContributor[name="<columnname>"]`.
- Search submit button: `[data-trigger="listSearch"]`.
- Row cells have **no** `data-name` — map columns by header text: find `thead th` whose text == label, read `td` at the **same index** (leading checkbox col is index 0 in both).

## Inline search mechanics (important)
- **Text fields**: type value + press `Enter` (keyCode 13) to submit. Prefer clicking `[data-trigger="listSearch"]` when overlays/`blockUI` are flaky.
- **Picklist/select2 fields**: selecting a value does **NOT** auto-submit (this instance has `autoRefreshListOnChange != '1'`; see `public/layouts/basic/modules/Base/resources/ListSearch.js` ~line 90). You must click `[data-trigger="listSearch"]` afterwards.
- After submit the list reloads via AJAX and the URL gets e.g. `search_params=[[["etap_sprzedazy","c","Aktywna"]]]` (operator may be `a`/`c`/…). Wait with `waitForLoadState('networkidle')` + table visible.
- **RecruitmentApplication**: open matching rows via `data-recordurl` / `hasText`, not blind `.first()`. Prefer `[data-trigger="listSearch"]` over Enter when overlays are flaky.

## WWW CV apply smoke (`tests/Www/`)

Full path: www.itconnect.pl JetForm → Cyberfolks → prod sync → test sync → cron A/B → assert on **`CRM_BASE_URL=https://test.itconnect.pl`**.

| Spec | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `apply-cv-smoke.spec.ts` | Browser submit + poll CRM (phase A + B) |
| `crm-import-verify.spec.ts` | CRM-only check (`E2E_KNOWN_NAME=…`) — no WWW |

Gotchas:
- Context **`locale: 'pl-PL'`** required. Headless default `en-US@posix` crashes JetForm `media.field.restrictions` (`Intl.NumberFormat`) → submit never fires (`validityState` null).
- CleanTalk: real mailbox only (default `bmankowski@itconnect.pl`); fake/`+tag` addresses → “Email does not exist”. Frequent submits → “forms too often” (cooldown before re-run).
- Uniqueness: timestamp in **name/message**, not email. CV fixture: `test-data/e2e-cv-min.pdf`.
- CV cron frequency on CRM is **60 s** (see `docker-commands.mdc`); file sync hops still add up to ~2 min without SSH trigger.

## select2 fields
Hidden selects carry class `select2-hidden-accessible` (1px box, not `display:none`). Drive them through the **native `<select>`** with Playwright `selectOption({ label }, { force: true })` — the list search reads the native `.val()`, so the select2 chip visuals don't matter.

## Discovering field/picklist/view data (MCP, read-only)
Use the `freecrm-mysql` MCP server (see `mcp-database-access.mdc`), not Docker shell:
- Fields of a module: `SELECT fieldname,columnname,uitype FROM vtiger_field WHERE tabid=<id>`.
- Picklist values: `SELECT <name> FROM vtiger_<name>` (e.g. `vtiger_etap_sprzedazy`).
- Custom views / saved filters: `vtiger_customview` (name, setdefault), columns in `vtiger_cvcolumnlist`, criteria in `vtiger_cvadvfilter`.
- `tabid` map: `user_privileges/tabdata.php`.

## Verifying live DOM
Inspect real selectors with the `cursor-ide-browser` MCP (navigate + `Runtime.evaluate`); CDP `Input.*` is denied — trigger handlers with element `.click()` inside `Runtime.evaluate` when refs go stale.

## Conventions
- Add the standard FreeCRM file header to new `.ts` files.
- Keep page objects thin and reusable; assert on data (e.g. every visible "Etap sprzedaży" cell == "Aktywna"), not just row counts.

## Module crawler

Regression sweep (not spec tests): `./crawl.sh` exports URLs then visits each with Playwright, watching `system.log`. See `error-checking.mdc` → Module crawler for commands, log levels, resume (`--start-from`), and output files.

DetailView tabs are exported per entity module (sample record + all `DETAILVIEWTAB` / `DETAILVIEWRELATED` links). Direct tab URL shape: `index.php?module=X&view=Detail&record=ID&mode=…&tab_label=…` — same params as `.related li[data-url]` on the detail page.
